Description_lang: Your damaging critical strikes grant you a stack of Preternatural Charge. When you reach $u stacks of Preternatural Charge, your next critical strike will consume all stacks to tear open a rift near your target, inflicting $s1 Arcane damage.
AuraDescription_lang: Reaching $u stacks will cause your next critical strike to consume Preternatural Charge, dealing Arcane damage.
